el-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/17-journalists-confirmed-dead-in-israel-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-4311-d614-abcf-eb7349530000</guid></item><item><title>以色列提供的数据显示，伊斯兰圣战组织火箭失灵袭击了加沙医院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-presents-data-showing-attack-on-gaza-hospital-caused-by-failed-islamic-jihad-rocket/0000018b-42d6-d259-a3bb-cef74fd70000</link><description>以色列军队展示了来自军队雷达系统、半岛电视台以及其他新闻媒体的视频记录，显示一枚错误的伊斯兰圣战火箭落在阿赫利医院附近，造成数百人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-presents-data-showing-attack-on-gaza-hospital-caused-by-failed-islamic-jihad-rocket/0000018b-42d6-d259-a3bb-cef74fd70000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列断水断电，加沙人面临脱水和疾病的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/with-no-water-or-electricity-from-israel-gazans-risk-dehydration-and-disease/0000018b-42ff-d614-abcf-eaff15d80000</link><description>即使在“平时”，加沙90%的自来水也无法饮用，战争期间情况变得更糟</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 14:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/with-no-water-or-electricity-from-israel-gazans-risk-dehydration-and-disease/0000018b-42ff-d614-abcf-eaff15d80000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯官方媒体称以色列在加沙的报复行动是“法西斯主义”，要求对撤离令实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/russian-media-calls-israeli-retaliation-in-gaza-fascism-demands-sanctions/0000018b-423e-d242-abef-523e7d060000</link><description>俄罗斯电视节目主持人将以色列与乌克兰进行比较，称加沙的行动是“令人震惊的残忍行为”；说不应该对以色列人“有一丝怜悯或同情”</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 11:16:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/russian-media-calls-israeli-retaliation-in-gaza-fascism-demands-sanctions/0000018b-423e-d242-abef-523e7d060000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯的恐怖视频：“我们在争取公众意识的斗争中落后了光年”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-are-light-years-behind-hamas-in-the-battle-for-public-consciousness/0000018b-3d0f-d07d-a99b-fdcf93100000</link><description>以色列传统媒体选择过滤哈马斯传播的可怕屠杀画面，但社交媒体却充斥着这样的画面。社交媒体将如何影响以色列的军事行动？图片如何改变了越南和黎巴嫩的战争进程？</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 10:59:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-are-light-years-behind-hamas-in-the-battle-for-public-consciousness/0000018b-3d0f-d07d-a99b-fdcf93100000</guid></item><item><title>创伤可以让以色列公众睁开眼睛。是时候组建和平内阁了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/trauma-can-open-the-israeli-publics-eyes-time-for-a-peace-cabinet/0000018b-4238-d242-abef-523e3eea0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 10:24:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/trauma-can-open-the-israeli-publics-eyes-time-for-a-peace-cabinet/0000018b-4238-d242-abef-523e3eea0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙医院爆炸后，伊斯坦布尔警方阻止袭击以色列领事馆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/istanbul-police-averts-attempt-to-storm-israeli-consulate-after-gaza-hospital-explosion/0000018b-4231-d242-abef-523752720000</link><description>伊斯坦布尔省长办公室称，周三早些时候，一群人用石头、棍棒和烟花袭击领事馆大楼，造成 60 多人受伤，其中大部分是警察</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 10:16:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/istanbul-police-averts-attempt-to-storm-israeli-consulate-after-gaza-hospital-explosion/0000018b-4231-d242-abef-523752720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队展示视频和音频显示伊斯兰圣战组织对加沙医院爆炸负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/israeli-army-presents-video-audio-to-show-islamic-jihad-behind-gaza-hospital-blast/0000018b-41f1-d242-abef-53f7d6570000</link><description>以色列国防军发言人播放哈马斯成员的录音，称这次爆炸是伊斯兰圣战组织发射失败的事件 ■ 拜登对内塔尼亚胡：看来是其他团队干的</description><pubD