z-cartoon/0000018b-4093-d881-abab-ed9be3410000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 02:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-4093-d881-abab-ed9be3410000</guid></item><item><title>在对以色列进行史无前例的战区访问时，拜登面临着与时间的赛跑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/on-unprecedented-warzone-visit-to-israel-biden-faces-a-race-against-time/0000018b-4047-df22-a5eb-497fc9ca0000</link><description>随着加沙地带人道主义灾难的发生、以色列和黎巴嫩边境的紧张局势以及阿拉伯领导人取消与他的会晤，美国总统的目标和行程迅速变化</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 01:13:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/on-unprecedented-warzone-visit-to-israel-biden-faces-a-race-against-time/0000018b-4047-df22-a5eb-497fc9ca0000</guid></item><item><title>“决心采取行动”：国会领导人承诺犹太组织全力支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/resolved-to-act-congressional-leaders-promise-jewish-groups-full-backing-for-israel/0000018b-4011-d242-abef-52372a5d0000</link><description>参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默誓言美国对以色列的紧急援助计划将“尽快”在国会获得通过</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 00:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/resolved-to-act-congressional-leaders-promise-jewish-groups-full-backing-for-israel/0000018b-4011-d242-abef-52372a5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列麦卡锡主义对其公民的迫害已经开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/israels-mccarthyite-persecution-of-its-own-citizens-has-begun/0000018b-3f1a-d2b8-a7db-ff7faf310000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 23:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/israels-mccarthyite-persecution-of-its-own-citizens-has-begun/0000018b-3f1a-d2b8-a7db-ff7faf310000</guid></item></channel></rss>